parameters:
\nw[Nonna]The selection of items here is good. It seems like
it would be easier if we prepare our equipment
before going to the dungeon.
\nw[Kuno]Nonna is so cautious. Thanks to her, we're saved.

\nw[Nonna]The outcome of a battle is determined by
preparation 90% of the time. So we mustn't be
lazy, okay?

\nw[Taro]I see you looking at a lot of armor, but do you
actually like weapons?

\nw[Nonna]If you ask me if I like it... I'm not sure. But
I've become knowledgeable about it because it's
necessary.

\nw[Nonna]I'll take care of the promotion here, so could you
please handle the promotion to the inn?
\nw[Taro]Speaking of Kuno, I wonder if she's okay?

\nw[Nonna]If it seems too difficult, I'm thinking of taking
over. But I don't want to become too
overprotective...
\nw[Weapon Shop]Please come and take a look at the Weapon Shop.
\nw[Weapon Shop]Please take care of us again.
\nw[Armor Shop]Please come again to the Armor Shop.
